      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "CODSTC"             to   f-key                  .
           move      rf-mgr-cod-pdc       to   rf-pdc-cod-pdc         .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofpdc"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
