      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                =    e-not-err
                     go to  let-arc-pdc-999.
       let-arc-pdc-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se non trovato                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   int-msg-err-000      thru int-msg-err-999        .
